aljevo]]'''\n| RD1-score1 = 2\n| RD1-seed2  = 2 (III E)\n| RD1-team2  = [[FK Sin\u0111eli\u0107 Ni\u0161|Sin\u0111eli\u0107 Ni\u0161]]\n| RD1-score2 = 1\n\n| RD1-seed3  = 2 ([[2007\u201308 Serbian League Belgrade|III B]])\n| RD1-team3  = [[FK Radni\u010dki Obrenovac|Radni\u010dki Obrenovac]]\n| RD1-score3 = 0 '''(2)'''\n| RD1-seed4  = 2 ([[2007\u201308 Serbian League Vojvodina|III V]])\n| RD1-team4  = '''[[FK In\u0111ija|In\u0111ija]]''' ([[Penalty shoot-out (association football)|p]])\n| RD1-score4 = 0 '''(4)'''\n\n| RD2-seed1  = 2 ([[2007\u201308 Serbian League West|III W]])\n| RD2-team1  = [[FK Sloga Kraljevo|Sloga Kraljevo]]\n| RD2-score1 = 0\n| RD2-seed2  = 2 ([[2007\u201308 Serbian League Vojvodina|III V]])\n| RD2-team2  = '''[[FK In\u0111ija|In\u0111ija]]'''\n| RD2-score2 = 2\n\n| RD3-seed1    = 2 ([[2007\u201308 Serbian League Vojvodina|III V]])\n| RD3-team1    = '''[[FK In\u0111ija|In\u0111ija]]'''\n| RD3-score1   = 2 1 '''3'''\n| RD3-score1-2 = \n| RD3-score1-A = \n| RD3-seed2    = 14 ([[2007\u201308 Serbian First League|II]])\n| RD3-team2    = [[FK Radni\u010dki Ni\u0161|Radni\u010dki Ni\u0161]]\n| RD3-score2   = 0 1 '''1'''\n| RD3-score2-2 = \n| RD3-score2-A = \n}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.fss.rs/ Football Association of Serbia]\n* [http://www.fsris.org.rs/ Football Association of East Serbia]\n\n{{Serbian League East}}\n{{2007\u201308 in Serbian football}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2007-08 Serbian League East}}\n[[Category:Serbian League East seasons]]\n[[Category:2007\u201308 in Serbian football leagues|3]]\n[[Category:2007\u201308 in European third tier association football leagues|Serbia]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football league season\n| competition      = Serbian League East\n| season           = 2007\u201308\n| winners          = [[FK Dinamo Vranje|Dinamo Vranje]]\n| promoted         = [[FK Dinamo Vranje|Dinamo Vranje]]\n| relegated        = [[OFK Ni\u0161]]<br/>[[FK Rudar Aleksinac|Rudar Aleksinac]]<br/>[[FK Ozren Sokobanja|Ozren Sokobanja]]<br/>[[FK Sloga Leskovac|Sloga Leskovac]]<br/>[[FK Trayal|Trayal]]<br/>[[FK Morava Vladi\u010din Han|Morava Vladi\u010din Han]]\n| matches          = \n| total goals      = \n| league topscorer = [[Novica Lazarevi\u0107]]\n| biggest home win = \n| biggest away win = \n| highest scoring  = \n| prevseason       = [[2006\u201307 Serbian League East|2006\u201307]]\n| nextseason       = [[2008\u201309 Serbian League East|2008\u201309]]\n}}\nThe '''2007\u201308''' [[Serbian League East]] season was the fifth season of the league under its current title. It began in August 2007 and ended in May 2008.\n\n==League table==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=PR\n\n|team1=DIN|name_DIN=[[FK Dinamo Vranje|Dinamo Vranje]]\n|team2=SIN|name_SIN=[[FK Sin\u0111eli\u0107 Ni\u0161|Sin\u0111eli\u0107 Ni\u0161]]\n|team3=DUB|name_DUB=[[FK Dubo\u010dica|Dubo\u010dica]]\n|team4=SVR|name_SVR=[[FK Svrljig|Svrljig]]\n|team5=KOP|name_KOP=[[FK Kopaonik|Kopaonik]]\n|team6=TIM|name_TIM=[[FK Timok|Timok]]\n|team7=BAL|name_BAL=Balkanski\n|team8=\u017dVB|name_\u017dVB=[[FK \u017delezni\u010dar Vranjska Banja|\u017delezni\u010dar Vranjska Banja]]\n|team9=\u017dUP|name_\u017dUP=[[FK \u017dupa|\u017dupa]]\n|team10=\u017dNI|name_\u017dNI=[[FK \u017delezni\u010dar Ni\u0161|\u017delezni\u010dar Ni\u0161]]\n|team11=MVH|name_MVH=[[FK Morava Vladi\u010din Han|Morava Vladi\u010din Han]]\n|team12=TRA|name_TRA=[[FK Trayal|Trayal]]\n|team13=SLO|name_SLO=[[FK Sloga Leskovac|Sloga Leskovac]]\n|team14=OZR|name_OZR=[[FK Ozren Sokobanja|Ozren Sokobanja]]\n|team15=RUD|name_RUD=[[FK Rudar Aleksinac|Rudar Aleksinac]]\n|team16=OFK|name_OFK=[[OFK Ni\u0161]]\n|win_DIN=19|draw_DIN=8|loss_DIN=3|gf_DIN=57|ga_DIN=21|status_DIN=C,P\n|win_SIN=18|draw_SIN=8|loss_SIN=4|gf_SIN=64|ga_SIN=25\n|win_DUB=18|draw_DUB=7|loss_DUB=5|gf_DUB=59|ga_DUB=19\n|win_SVR=17|draw_SVR=4|loss_SVR=9|gf_SVR=48|ga_SVR=28\n|win_KOP=15|draw_KOP=9|loss_KOP=6|gf_KOP=45|ga_KOP=27|adjust_points_KOP=-1\n|win_TIM=12|draw_TIM=7|loss_TIM=11|gf_T